# Frontend Patterns

## Component Patterns
- Composition over inheritance
- Compound components with Context
- Render props for data loading
- `React.memo` for pure components

## Custom Hooks
- `useToggle`, `useDebounce`, `useQuery`
- Extract reusable logic from components

## Performance
- `useMemo`/`useCallback` for memoization
- `lazy()`/`Suspense` for code splitting
- `@tanstack/react-virtual` for long lists

## Accessibility
- Keyboard navigation (ArrowDown/Up/Enter/Escape)
- Focus management in modals
- ARIA roles and attributes

---

# Backend Patterns

## Architecture
- Repository pattern (abstract data access)
- Service layer (business logic separate from data)
- Middleware pattern (auth, rate limiting)
- Centralized error handler with `ApiError` class

## Database
- Select only needed columns
- Batch fetch to prevent N+1 queries
- Transactions for multi-table operations
- Cache-aside pattern with Redis

## Error Handling
- Exponential backoff retry
- Structured logging (JSON format)
- Generic error messages to users, detailed in server logs

